title: Stonechat
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Irish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers some vegetarian dishes and 2 vegan items which are a tofu dish and a stir fry of vegetables in sweet chili sauce. Other veggie options include hummus plate, usually vegan soup of the day. Will substitute the non vegan Irish soda bread for vegan pita bread.
